01:05.851 --> 01:07.783
- Richard Evans.
- Poppy Langmore.

01:07.818 --> 01:08.555
<i>She's Alice.</i>

01:08.557 --> 01:10.757
Maddie was impersonating
Poppy to become Alice.

01:10.759 --> 01:12.459
She was, like, doing a version of her.

01:12.461 --> 01:14.594
- Oh, dear.
- This is the actual Alice.

01:14.596 --> 01:16.129
Except I'm actually rich.

01:16.131 --> 01:18.331
Okay, Sophia gets here
in an hour and a half.

01:18.333 --> 01:20.200
Okay, guys, we got to go.

01:20.202 --> 01:21.535
Got to go now. Come on.

01:21.537 --> 01:24.070
_

01:24.071 --> 01:25.718
_

01:31.208 --> 01:33.613
What does the Doctor want?
How angry is he?

01:33.615 --> 01:35.382
It's time for you to come
in and see the Doctor.

01:35.384 --> 01:37.818
Look, I did it, and I'm still breathing.

01:40.480 --> 01:41.421
I'll take it.

