02:20.829 --> 02:22.729
<i>[music cuts in and out]</i>

02:22.731 --> 02:24.764
<i>[various voices and music over radio]</i>

02:24.766 --> 02:27.534
<i>Central Pennsylvania's
rock-and-roll time machine,</i>

02:27.536 --> 02:29.202
<i>WURG,</i>

02:29.204 --> 02:31.238
<i>coming to you out of Pottsville.</i>

02:31.240 --> 02:37.544
<i>♪ When you're young
and so in love as we ♪</i>

02:37.546 --> 02:41.882
