[sighs]

11:54.655 --> 11:56.318
Dude, I thought we were goners.

11:56.320 --> 11:57.853
I thought they were gonna shoot us.

11:57.855 --> 11:59.154
What?

11:59.156 --> 12:02.224
This is what immigration is like?

12:02.226 --> 12:06.461
<i>Dude, this is a major issue.</i>

12:06.463 --> 12:09.464
<i>[soft music]</i>

12:09.466 --> 12:15.203
<i>♪ ♪</i>

12:15.205 --> 12:16.505
- Hey, Mom.
- [gasps]

12:16.576 --> 12:20.742
Oh, God. Oh.

12:20.744 --> 12:22.677
Hi, Maddie.

12:22.679 --> 12:25.480
Hey.

12:31.155 --> 12:34.356
You changed your hair.

12:34.358 --> 12:36.825
Some things still come for you.

12:36.827 --> 12:40.529
Maybe you should have
them forwarded to Houston.

12:47.734 --> 12:51.573
Sad not having you at
Christmas this year.

12:51.575 --> 12:53.809
I know. I'm sorry about that.

12:53.811 --> 12:55.510
It's quiet.

12:55.512 --> 12:57.212
We missed you.

12:58.749 --> 13:00.649
I missed you too.

13:04.922 --> 13:07.389
Mom, I need to tell you something.

13:07.391 --> 13:09.224
It's important.

13:13.864 --> 13:16.398
I don't live in Houston.

13:16.400 --> 13:18.300
I never did.

13:18.302 --> 13:21.069
And I don't work for UNICEF.

13:21.071 --> 13:23.772
Okay.

13:26.844 --> 13:29.811
Well, aren't you gonna say something?

13:29.813 --> 13:32.447
How are you making money?

13:32.449 --> 13:36.351
Just job to job, really.

13:38.155 --> 13:39.821
Job to job.

13:39.823 --> 13:42.691
Yeah, I've been, um,

13:42.693 --> 13:45.460
just figuring it out.

13:45.462 --> 13:47.796
I'm sure that sounds flaky to you,

13:47.798 --> 13:50.799
just like everything else I've done.

13:50.801 --> 13:53.802
I never thought working
for UNICEF sounded flaky.

13:56.440 --> 13:58.473
Is there anything else
you want to tell me?

14:03.480 --> 14:07.482
Just that I'm sorry
for not being honest.

14:08.221 --> 14:10.285
Yes.

14:11.788 --> 14:14.489
Thanks for saying so.

14:17.961 --> 14:19.427
Dad in his room?

14:19.429 --> 14:20.441
Asleep, as usual.

14:20.464 --> 14:24.766
But please wait until he's up to say hi.

14:24.768 --> 14:26.301
You staying the night?

14:26.303 --> 14:29.871
- Is that okay?
- Of course.

14:29.873 --> 14:32.841
Okay.

14:32.843 --> 14:39.915
